channel.title: [C4D] rocket
channel.description:
Well I have decided to put the mountain on hold till I know more about how I will go about finishing it so two days ago I started to read a basic modeling tutorial and it taught me how to make a bit about materials, lighting, and of course basic modeling. This is basically a toy rocket, something a kid would play with.
[img]http://i242.photobucket.com/albums/ff141/archer98/rocket7.jpg[/img]
[img]http://i242.photobucket.com/albums/ff141/archer98/rocket8.jpg[/img]
[img]http://i242.photobucket.com/albums/ff141/archer98/rocket.jpg[/img]
Before you say "its to square" I am aware of that, I didn't want it to look like your everyday rocket.
